Class ApplicantController

Object
UserController
ApplicantController
Direct Known Subclasses:
HDBOfficerController
public class ApplicantController extends UserController
Controller handling applicant-specific operations in the BTO management system. This controller manages the user interface and business logic for applicant users, including BTO project viewing, application submission, enquiry management, and flat booking requests. It extends the base UserController class and implements the applicant-specific menu system and workflows.
Version:
1.0
Author:
BTOMS Team
